    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, pampered and kept tucked away in a garage its whole life. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found anywhere. If you're looking for total perfection and a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you! I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself!",
