      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Meticulously maintained, this example features documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and mechanical integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, feeding power through the factory Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is exceptionally tight, retaining its original suspension geometry and staggered forged alloy wheels. With flawless factory paint and a pristine Nappa leather cabin, this is a turnkey specimen for the purist enthusiast.",
